# GENERATE_FLOWS provider — pick one, or omit to auto-detect.
#
# Auto-detection order: Claude CLI → Anthropic SDK → OpenAI → Gemini
#
# Option 1 — Claude CLI (uses your Claude.ai subscription, no API key required).
# Install: https://claude.ai/download  |  verify: claude --version
# No env var needed — auto-detected if 'claude' is in PATH.
#
# Set this to skip CLI detection (useful in CI where claude is installed
# but you want an API-key-based provider instead):
# STF_DISABLE_CLAUDE_CLI=1
#
# Option 2 — Anthropic SDK (billed to your Anthropic API account)
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your-key-here
#
# Option 3 — OpenAI / Codex
# OPENAI_API_KEY=your-key-here
#
# Option 4 — Gemini (use a real model ID, not bare 'gemini')
# GEMINI_API_KEY=your-key-here
# FLOW_MODEL=gemini-1.5-pro
#
# Option 5 — Ollama (local, no API key)
# FLOW_MODEL=ollama:llama3

# --- Your product adapter vars go below this line ---
# APP_URL=http://localhost:3000
# APP_API_KEY=your-api-key
